16
17 (C) THE CATEGORIES OF THIRD PARTIES AND SPECIFIC AFFILIATES WITH WHOM THE MEDICAL PREGNANCY
18 CENTER AND PREGNANCY CENTER SHARES THE CONSUMER HEALTH DATA; AND
19
20 (D) HOW A CONSUMER MAY EXERCISE THEIR RIGHTS TO PROTECT THIS INFORMATION.
21 (2) A MEDICAL PREGNANCY CENTER OR A PREGNANCY CENTER SHALL PROMINENTLY PUBLISH A LINK TO ITS
22 CONSUMER HEALTH DATA PRIVACY POLICY ON ITS HOMEPAGE.
